Package com.codenvy.example.swing

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InfoHashGen
    InfoHashGen generates the 20-byte SHA1 encoded hash of the info dictionary in the torrent file.
    MetaInfo
    MetaInfo parses the torrent file to extract necessary fields and data
    PeerConnection
    Peer Connection class handles connection to and communicating with peers on a seperate thread
    TrackerProtocol
    TrackerProtocol sends the initial request to the tracker to get the list of peers for this torrent and parses the response.
